{"tid":603026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"官斥警方律政司「高度無能無知」","createTime":"2018-03-23T11:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T11:38:17.000Z","uid":30647,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c08cd520f5edc5bf52b0640c9c130c7ab81d90f","tid":603026,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無搜查令擅扣塑料公司貨物逾兩年半　官斥警方律政司「高度無能無知」 <br />\n<br />\n方於2008年調查一宗懷疑開空頭支票騙取貨品的案件時，在無展示搜查令下擅自扣起一家塑料公司的17櫃貨物，直至逾兩年半後才將最後的6櫃貨還給塑料公司。該塑料公司指警方的行動屬濫權及無視法律，早前入稟高等法院向警務處長及律政司長索償。高院法官今頒下判辭，<span style=\"color: red;\">斥責警方及律政司所為顯示出他們的高度無能及無知</span>，又指律政司的部分僱員處理本案時的水平，明顯遠低於公眾期望，終裁定塑料公司可獲176萬元賠償<br />\n<br />\nlink 有全文<br />\nsource <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180323/s00001/1521797936604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180323%2Fs00001%2F1521797936604&d=UMigsLiDAYQDA6SGr28idpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d3dc331f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180323%2Fs00001%2F1521797936604&h=b7de20b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180323/s00001/1521797936604</a>"},{"pid":"5886d85d6712a57a1e374bce4f932e02fb5467fa","tid":603026,"uid":30647,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180323/s00001/36229a5da563c60fa774680d8fa32c57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180323%2Fs00001%2F36229a5da563c60fa774680d8fa32c57.jpg&h=646be321&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59249aaaf865ed93c5a295cdc3d02dc747489cab","tid":603026,"uid":56900,"like":10,"dislike":0